25%20complete%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcrggxgl1k0xo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20told%20BBC%20News.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20might%20have%20been%20surprised%20to%20learn%20that%20Sotheby's%20believes%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc39df8ae52d6ecfabefa05edbb6284cfb14dd18a6690a96129997f0425c1655a%26postID%3D66598d0166bb31e507521b45%26postSlug%3Dman-finds-dinosaur-skeleton-on-walk-could-get-millions-auction-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sothebys.com%252Fen%252Fbuy%252Fauction%252F2024%252Fnatural-history%252Fstegosaurus%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecould%20fetch%20up%20to%20%246%20million%20at%20auction.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApex%20is%20%26quot%3Bvirtually%20complete%26quot%3B%20and%20well%20preserved%2C%20with%20274%20possible%20bone%20elements%20mounted%20on%20a%20steel%20armature%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dc39df8ae52d6ecfabefa05edbb6284cfb14dd18a6690a96129997f0425c1655a%26postID%3D66598d0166bb31e507521b45%26postSlug%3Dman-finds-dinosaur-skeleton-on-walk-could-get-millions-auction-2024-5%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.sothebys.com%252Fen%252Fbuy%252Fauction%252F2024%252Fnatural-history%252Fstegosaurus%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESotheby's%20said%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20auction%20house's%20global%20head%20of%20science%20and%20popular%20culture%2C%20Cassandra%20Hatton%2C%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20best%20fossils%20of%20its%20kind%20ever%20unearthed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApex%20will%20be%20auctioned%20in%20July%20during%20Sotheby's%20annual%20%26quot%3BGeek%20Week%26quot%3B%20sale.%20It's%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20%244-6%20million%2C%20with%20the%20auction%20house%20describing%20it%20as%20one%20of%20the%20%26qu