ich%20causes%20complete%20hair%20loss%20since%20her%20teens.%20I%20asked%20why%20she%20had%20stopped%20wearing%20wigs%2C%20and%20she%20said%20that%20it%20took%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20she%20became%20more%20comfortable%20showing%20up%20completely%20herself.%20I%20hoped%20to%20be%20that%20confident%20someday.%20That%20kind%20of%20vulnerability%20gives%20others%20strength.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20a%20year%20later%2C%20it%20had%20gotten%20much%20easier%2C%20but%20not%20without%20moments%20of%20frustration.%20One%20day%2C%20I%20received%20an%20unsolicited%20iPhoto%20memory%20from%20seven%20years%20ago.%20In%20the%20photo%2C%20I%20was%20mid-laugh%2C%20my%20natural%20long%20and%20lustrous%20hair%20tossed%20over%20my%20left%20shoulder.%20I%20went%20down%20a%20sad%2C%20nostalgic%20rabbit%20hole%20looking%20over%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-vs-old-photo-portrait-comparison-100-years-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eold%20photos%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20wishing%20I'd%20appreciated%20what%20I'd%20had%20while%20I'd%20had%20it.%20I%20used%20to%20always%20compare%20my%20hair%20to%20others'.%20It%20wasn't%20thick%20enough%20and%20didn't%20grow%20fast%20enough.%20Now%2C%20if%20I%20had%20my%20old%20hair%20back%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20change%20a%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20began%20to%20enjoy%20wearing%20different%20wigs%2C%20dating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cs%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fs%3E%3Cspan%3Epost-hair%20loss%20was%20scary.%20My%20first%20date%20wearing%20a%20wig%20proved%20nerve-racking.%20I%20wondered%20if%20he%20could%20tell%20and%20it%20took%20me%20two%20hours%20to%20get%20ready%20and%20choose%20a%20wig.%20Yet%2C%20as%20the%20night%20wore%20on%2C%20I%20didn't%20think%20about%20my%20wig%20at%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20hard%20part%20was%20confessing%20the%20truth%20after%20a%20few%20dates.%20I%20w