y%20suit%20cracking%20and%20my%20arms%20ripping%20out%20of%20their%20sockets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rosolie%20recalled%20that%20he%20was%20inches%20away%20from%20having%20his%20rib%20cage%20explode.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20all%20about%20showing%20people%20the%20power%20of%20these%20snakes%20with%20the%20mission%20of%20protecting%20their%20habitats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnacondas%20are%20a%20group%20of%20large%20boas%20that%20are%20found%20in%20tropical%20South%20America.%20They%20are%20known%20to%20kill%20their%20prey%20by%20constricting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20you%20exhale%2C%20you%20never%20get%20that%20space%20back%2C%20you%20never%20take%20that%20breath%20in%20again.%20So%20you%20exhale%20and%20the%20snake%20squeezes%2C%20and%20then%20when%20you%20try%20to%20breathe%20in%2C%20there's%20nothing.%20And%20so%20I%20couldn't%20even%20call%20for%20help.%20It%20was%20terrifying%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Mr%20Rosolie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20National%20Geographic%2C%20when%20taking%20into%20account%20both%20weight%20and%20length%2C%20the%20green%20anaconda%20is%20the%20largest%20snake%20in%20the%20world%2C%20growing%20up%20to%20nine%20metres%20long%20and%20weighing%20as%20much%20as%20227%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717146720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fdijrppuo_paul-rosolie-anaconda-instagram_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fman-describes-how-it-was-like-to-be-eaten-alive-by-anaconda-ribs-exploded-5785992%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anacondas%20are%20a%20group%20of%20large%20boas%20that%20are%20found%20in%20tropical%20South%20America.%20They%20are%20known%20to%20kill%20their%20prey%20by%20constricting%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fman-describes-how-it-was-like-to-be-eaten-alive-by-anaconda-ribs-exploded-5785992%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fman-describes-how-it-was-like-to-be-eaten-alive-by-anaconda-ribs-exploded-5785992%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fman-describes-how-it-was-like-to-be-eaten-alive-by-anaconda-ribs-exploded-5785992%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Make%20Farming%20Profitable%3F%20Himachal%20Couple%20Earn%20Double%20with%2025%20Kinds%20of%20Crops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20almost%20midnight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjit%20Singh%20was%20half-asleep%20when%20his%20wife%2C%20Jaswinder%2C%20woke%20him%20up%20and%20reminded%20him%20about%20the%20workshop%20on%20natural%20farming.%20He%20wondered%20what%20she%20was%20yapping%20about%20and%20went%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%20when%20Ranjit%20enquired%2C%20he%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F55881%2Fzero-budget-natural-farming-subash-palekar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESubhash%20Palekar%20Natural%20Farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eworkshop%20that%20could%20benefit%20the%20couple%20immensely.%20On%20her%20advice%2C%20he%20immediately%20left%20for%20Solan%2C%20150%20km%20away%20from%20his%20village%20in%20Kanshipur%2C%20Sirmaur%2C%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%2C%20Ranjit%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20on%20farming%20took%20a%20complete%20U-turn.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20decades%2C%20we%20had%20been%20growing%20crops%20using%20chemical%20fertilisers%20like%20urea%2C%20weedicides%2C%20and%20chemical%20insecticides.%20I%20never%20knew%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20harm%20that%20we%20were%20causing%20ourselves%20and%20to%20those%20buying%20crops%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2057-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20inorganic%20farming%20a%20sin%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20convert%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20(1.4%20acre)%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20training%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20growing%20crops%20on%20a%20small%20part%20of%20our%20land%20using%20natural%20farming%2C%20but%20later%2C%20I%20swore%20never%20to%20use%20any%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20the%20field%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351657%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month-long%20training%2C%20Ranjit%20returned%20to%20his%20wife%20with%20secret%20tips%20and%20techniques%20of%20natural%20farming.%20Jaswinder%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20training%20that%20could%20have%20convinced%20her%20husband%20to%20shift%20to%20natural%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202018%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20been%20cultivating%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20including%20lemons%2C%20moringa%2C%20Caprica%20chilies%2C%20pomegranate%2C%20sugarcane%2C%20turmeric%2C%20wheat%2C%20paddy%2C%20guavas%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20spinach%2C%20onions%2C%20beetroot%2C%20ginger%2C%20carrot%2C%20and%20more%20through%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197256%2Ftelangana-couple-zero-budget-natural-farming-organic-mango-navara-rice-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20budget%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EZero%20input%20cost%2C%20double%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Jaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%2C%20using%20chemicals%20to%20boost%20production%20from%20the%20field%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20farm.%20But%20the%20soil%20kept%20asking%20for%20more.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20noticed%20that%20our%20fertiliser%20usage%20kept%20increasing%20every%20year.%20Initially%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20grow%20our%20produce%20using%205-7%20kg%20of%20urea%2C%20however%2C%20we%20were%20later%20forced%20to%20add%2010-12%20kg%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20there%20were%20additional%20input%20costs%20for%20recurring%20fertiliser%20and%20pesticide%20usage.%20The%20input%20costs%20for%20us%20were%20Rs%202%2C000%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20a%20season.%20Now%2C%20this%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20zero%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20there%20are%20zero%20production%20costs%20in%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming.%20It%20is%20the%20practice%20of%20growing%20crops%20that%20eliminates%20the%20application%20of%20chemical%20inputs%20like%20urea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20advantages%20of%20natural%20farming%2C%20the%20first%20one%20being%20the%20availability%20of%20toxin-free%20food%20and%20rejuvenated%20soil%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaswinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%20converted%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-3-1717133467-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJaswinder%20and%20Ranjit%20converted%20their%20entire%20seven-bigha%20land%20into%20a%20natural%20farm.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20year%20of%20application%2C%20the%20production%20for%20the%20couple%20was%20one-third%20less%20than%20the%20inorganic%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20not%20demotivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20losses%20in%20the%20initial%20years.%20People%20would%20comment%20how%20we%20incurred%20losses%20switching%20to%20natural%20farming%20but%20we%20were%20happy%20to%20incur%20these%20instead%20of%20spending%20lakhs%20in%20medical%20treatments%20from%20eating%20toxic%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20them%201.5%20years%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%2C%20the%20couple%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20get%20three%20quintals%20of%20produce%20per%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20advantages%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321571%2Famith-kishan-quits-job-to-start-hebbuvu-organic-and-natural-farming-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20that%20although%20the%20production%20is%20the%20same%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20this%20produce%20is%20double.%20For%20instance%2C%20our%20wheat%20is%20sold%20at%20Rs%204%2C000%20whereas%20the%20inorganic%20wheat%20is%20for%20Rs%202%2C200%20per%20quintal.%20Similarly%2C%20our%20sugar%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100%2C%20compared%20to%20Rs%2050-60%20per%20kg%20from%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20zero%20cost%20of%20production%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20doubled%20their%20income%20from%20Rs%2055%2C000%20to%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20by%20selling%20vegetables%20and%20fruits.%20Their%20produce%20has%20earned%20a%20huge%20demand%20among%20the%20local%20schools%2C%20teachers%2C%20and%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswinder%20also%20processes%20the%20low-grade%20vegetables%20into%20pickles%2C%20vinegar%2C%20and%20chutneys.%20Annually%2C%20she%20processes%20up%20to%20eight%20quintals%20of%20vegetables%20like%20lemons%2C%20cauliflower%2C%20reddish%2C%20beetroot%2C%20and%20ginger%20into%20value-added%20products.%20This%20earns%20them%20an%20additional%20income%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20cultivates%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20through%20natural%20farming.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1717133355-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20cultivates%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20grains%2C%20and%20spices%20through%20natural%20farming.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBijamrit%2C%20brahmastra%2C%20agnihastra%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20components%20of%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20buying%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20insecticides%2C%20the%20couple%20makes%20their%20own%20natural%20products%20using%20simple%20ingredients%20like%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%2C%20and%20agro-waste%20like%20leaves%20and%20jaggery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20make%20%3Cem%3Ebijamrit%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20is%20a%20formulation%20of%20cow%20dung%2C%20urine%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Echuna%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lime).%20It%20is%20used%20to%20treat%20seeds%20before%20sowing.%20After%20germination%2C%20which%20takes%20about%2015%20days%2C%20we%20fertiliise%20the%20soil%20with%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20technique%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jaswinder%20asks%20to%20start%20with%20five%20kg%20of%20cow%20dung%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20seven%20litres%20of%20cow%20urine%20in%20a%20200-litre%20drum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20this%2C%20add%201.5%20kg%20of%20%3Cem%3Ebesan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20flour)%20and%20jaggery%20each.%20Fill%20the%20water%20to%20the%20rim%20and%20stir%20the%20mixture.%20Take%2040%20litres%20of%20%3Cem%3Ejivamrit%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20fertilise%20one%20%3Cem%3Ebigha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Ranjit%20shares%20his%20secrets%20to%20preparing%20natural%20insecticides%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmastra%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eagnihastra%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20enhance%20plant%20disease%20resistance%2C%20provide%20nutrients%2C%20and%20control%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20make%20%3Cem%3Ebrahmastra%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Etake%20one%20kg%20of%20four%20kinds%20of%20leaves%20and%20neem.%20Crush%20them%20and%20add%20in%20four%20litres%20of%20cow%20urine%20and%20dung.%20Boil%20the%20mixture.%20After%20two%20boils%2C%20cool%20it%20down%20and%20strain%20it%20into%20a%20tank.%20It%20will%20be%20ready%20to%20be%20sprayed%20on%20crops%20after%2048%20hours.%20You%20can%20also%20store%20this%20insecticide%20for%20six%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20makes%20their%20own%20natural%20fertilisers%20using%20simple%20ingredients%20like%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-1-1717133339-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20makes%20their%20own%20natural%20fertilisers%20using%20simple%20ingredients%20like%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20insects%20are%20still%20not%20controlled%2C%20we%20use%20our%20%3Cem%3Eagnihastra.%20%3C%2Fem%3EIt%20is%20prepared%20using%20spicy%20green%20chillies%2C%20peppers%2C%20and%20garlic.%20It%20is%20sure%20to%20control%20pest%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaswinder%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20the%20natural%20fertilisers%2C%20ensure%20to%20make%20the%20%3Cem%3Emedh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(field%20boundary)%20wall%20higher%20so%20that%20chemical%20water%20from%20neighbouring%20fields%20does%20not%20seep%20into%20your%20soil.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20received%20immense%20recognition%20for%20their%20work.%20In%20April%20this%20year%2C%20they%20were%20awarded%20by%20the%20Agriculture%20University%20of%20Sirmour.%20On%20the%20occasion%20of%20the%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%20in%202022%2C%20they%20were%20honoured%20by%20the%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Sirmaur%2C%20IAS%20Sumit%20Khimta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20small%20farmers%20who%20are%20receiving%20so%20much%20recognition.%20It%20is%20a%20big%20achievement%20for%20us.%20We%20never%20knew%20we%20would%20get%20opportunities%20to%20address%20thousands%20of%20people%20in%20front%20of%20the%20officials%20like%20the%20governor%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaswinder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20recognition%2C%20Jaswinder%20takes%20pride%20in%20receiving%20compliments%20from%20her%20guests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20if%20I%20ignored%20the%20%3Cem%3Ephulke%20%3C%2Fem%3E(wheat%20chapati)%20for%20some%20time%2C%20they%20would%20harden%20and%20dry%20out.%20But%20those%20prepared%20from%20the%20naturally%20grown%20wheat%20remain%20soft.%20We%20get%20lots%20of%20praise%20from%20guests%20for%20the%20taste%20and%20aroma%20of%20our%20chapati%20and%20vegetables.%20When%20asked%2C%20we%20tell%20them%20the%20magic%20behind%20it%20is%20natural%20farming!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Ranjit%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717146517000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fhimachal-2-1717133412.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351525%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20Jaswinder%20Kaur%20and%20Ranjit%20Singh%20from%20Himachal%20have%20been%20using%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming%20to%20cultivate%20at%20least%2025%20kinds%20of%20crops.%20Here's%20how%20they%20made%20farming%20profitable%20and%20train%20others%20around%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20court%20extends%20detention%20of%20Russian-US%20journalist%20Kurmasheva%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717146456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110590373%2Cimgsize-20380.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-court-extends-detention-of-russian-us-journalist-kurmasheva%2Farticleshow%2F110590236.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%