%20We%20are%20fighting%20against%20tyranny%2C%20and%20if%20I%20have%20to%20sacrifice%20my%20life%20for%20the%20country%2C%20do%20not%20mourn%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20today.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20said%20his%20health%20had%20deteriorated%20significantly%20during%20his%2050-day%20imprisonment%2C%20resulting%20in%20substantial%20weight%20loss%20and%20ongoing%20health%20concerns.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20denied%20medication%20for%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20jail%20for%2050%20days%2C%20and%20in%20those%2050%20days%2C%20I%20lost%206%20kilos...%20Even%20after%20being%20released%2C%20I%20have%20not%20regained%20my%20weight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shared%2C%20adding%20that%20doctors%20are%20now%20concerned%20about%20his%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20despite%20these%20challenges%2C%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20remains%20his%20top%20priority.%20He%20promised%20that%20essential%20services%20and%20initiatives%20such%20as%20free%20electricity%2C%20Mohalla%20clinics%2C%20hospitals%2C%20free%20medicines%2C%20and%20women's%20free%20bus%20travel%20would%20continue%20unabated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20I%20won't%20be%20among%20you%2C%20do%20not%20worry.%20All%20your%20work%20will%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20may%20not%20be%20with%20you%20physically%2C%20but%20your%20work%20will%20not%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20also%20made%20an%20emotional%20plea%20for%20the%20well-being%20of%20his%20elderly%20parents%20and%20urged%20the%20public%20to%20keep%20them%20in%20their%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20are%20very%20old...%20If%20you%20pray%20for%20my%20mother%20daily%2C%20she%20will%20surely%20remain%20healthy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20now-scrapped%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20believes%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20and%20seeking%20bribes%2C%20or%20kickbacks%2C%20in%20return%20for%20liquor%20licences.%20The%20agency%20has%20claimed%20the%20AAP%20received%20kickbacks%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20that%20were%20then%20used%20to%20fund%20its%20Goa%20and%20Punjab%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20refused%20all%20charges%20and%20called%20the%20arrest%20and%20case%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B%2C%20coming%20as%20it%20did%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%20The%20arrest%20also%20triggered%20a%20political%20spat%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20of%20which%20the%20AAP%20is%20a%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717143000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F18j4b8kc_arvind-kejriwal-_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-do-not-mourn-message-for-supporters-ahead-of-surrender-at-tihar-jail-5785229%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20that%20he%20would%20leave%20his%20house%20at%203%20pm%20on%20Sunday%20to%20surrender%20as%20the%20interim%20bail%20granted%20to%20him%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20a%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20ends.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-do-not-mourn-message-for-supporters-ahead-of-surrender-at-tihar-jail-5785229%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-do-not-mourn-message-for-supporters-ahead-of-surrender-at-tihar-jail-5785229%2Famp%2F