rotection%20to%20an%20interfaith%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20law%20does%20not%20permit%20a%20Muslim%20man's%20marriage%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bfire-worshipper%26quot%3B%2C%20Justice%20GS%20Ahluwalia%20said%20while%20hearing%20a%20petition%20by%20the%20couple%20seeking%20police%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafee%20Khan%20and%20Sarika%20Sen%20told%20the%20court%20they%20wished%20to%20marry%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20which%20allows%20marriages%20irrespective%20of%20the%20faith%20or%20religion%20followed%20by%20the%20groom%20and%20the%20bride%2C%20but%20couldn't%20do%20so%20due%20to%20threats%20from%20their%20family.%20They%20sought%20security%20for%20their%20safe%20appearance%20before%20the%20marriage%20registrar%20and%20protection%20from%20any%20criminal%20charges%20(like%20kidnapping)%20filed%20by%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20also%20asserted%20they%20wouldn't%20convert%20and%20that%20their%20marriage%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20would%20override%20restrictions%20under%20the%20personal%20law.%20Sarika%20will%20remain%20a%20Hindu%20and%20Safee%20a%20Muslim%20and%20won't%20interfere%20with%20each%20other's%20religious%20practices%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20family%2C%20who%20opposed%20their%20petition%2C%20alleged%20that%20she%20had%20eloped%20with%20family%20jewellery%20and%20cash%2C%20and%20that%20interfaith%20marriage%20would%20lead%20them%20to%20societal%20ostracism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20both%20sides%20and%20examining%20relevant%20precedents%2C%20the%20court%20said%20a%20marriage%20between%20a%20Muslim%20man%20and%20an%20idol-worshipping%20woman%20is%20considered%20irregular%2C%20though%20not%20void.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20per%20Mahomedan%20law%2C%20the%20marriage%20of%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20with%20a%20girl%20who%20is%20an%20idolatress%20or%20a%20fire-worshipper%20is%20not%20a%20valid%20marriage.%20Even%20if%20the%20marriage%20is%20registered%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20the%20marriage%20would%20be%20no%20more%20a%20valid%20marriage%20and%20it%20would%20be%20an%20irregular%20(fasid)%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Ahluwalia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20highlighted%20the%20difference%20between%20valid%20(sahih)%2C%20void%20(batil)%2C%20and%20irregular%20(fasid)%20marriages%20in%20Muslim%20law%2C%20referencing%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20interpretation%20in%20Mohammed%20Salim%20vs%20Shamsudeen%20and%20other%20authoritative%20texts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinding%20no%20grounds%20for%20granting%20police%20protection%20or%20other%20reliefs%20to%20the%20couple%2C%20it%20dismissed%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717142940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F9644rg78_madhya-pradesh-high-court_625x300_02_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-invalid-under-muslim-personal-law-high-court-5785523%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20marriage%20between%20a%20Muslim%20man%20and%20a%20Hindu%20woman%20is%20not%20valid%20under%20Muslim%20personal%20law%20even%20if%20registered%20under%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20while%20denying%20police%20protection%20to%20an%20interfaith%20couple.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-invalid-under-muslim-personal-law-high-court-5785523%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-invalid-under-muslim-personal-law-high-court-5785523%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finterfaith-marriage-invalid-under-muslim-personal-law-high-court-5785523%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Seasonal%20Adventures%20With%20Myntra%3A%20Get%20Minimum%2020%25%20Off%20On%20Bi