3EMore%20encouraging%20this%20year%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20with%20the%20improved%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20and%20the%20prevailing%20peace%2C%20foreign%20tourists%20have%20started%20coming%20to%20Kashmir%20in%20good%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20earn%20foreign%20exchange%20once%20the%20foreign%20tourists%20start%20coming%20to%20Kashmir.%20In%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20most%20of%20the%20foreign%20tourists%20are%20high-end%20tourists%20whose%20average%20spending%20during%20their%20stay%20is%20more%20than%20the%20average%20domestic%20tourists.%20Not%20that%20the%20domestic%20tourists%20do%20not%20include%20high-end%20guests.%20The%20few%205-star%20hotels%20we%20have%20in%20the%20Valley%20are%20also%20completely%20sold%20out%20these%20days%20and%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20guests%20are%20domestic%20spenders%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Hoteliers%20Club%20of%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENormally%20the%20tourist%20arrivals%20start%20coming%20down%20with%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20annual%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20rush%20of%20pilgrims%20who%20come%20for%20'Darshan'%20at%20the%20cave%20shrine%20situated%203888%20metres%20above%20sea%20level%20in%20Kashmir%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20starts%20on%20June%2029%20and%20will%20conclude%20after%2052%20days%20on%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHoteliers%20believe%20that%20given%20the%20number%20of%20bookings%20being%20made%20presently%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20the%20tourist%20arrivals%20would%20be%20affected%20by%20the%20ensuing%20Amarnath%20Yatra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20the%20unlikely%20fall%20in%20the%20number%20of%20tourist%20arrivals%20this%20year%20in%20Kashmir%20is%20the%20soaring%20temperature%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20of%20course%20other%20hill%20stations%20like%20Shimla%2C%20Darjeeling%20and%20Nainital%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20match%20the%20tourist%20uptake%20capacity%20of%20Kashmir%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20a%20local%20tour%20and%20travel%20operator%20who%20has%20been%20in%20business%20for%20more%20than%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20tourists%20are%20mainly%20coming%20to%20the%20Valley%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Maharashtra.%20Local%20tour%20and%20travel%20operators%20say%20the%20tourist%20flow%20from%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20will%20start%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tourism%20industry%20is%20the%20second%20main%20industry%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20horticulture.%20While%20horticulture%20is%20believed%20to%20generate%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20for%20the%20local%20economy%2C%20the%20tourism%20industry%20is%20believed%20to%20pump%20in%20another%20Rs%208000%20crore%20annually%20into%20the%20local%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20earnings%20from%20horticulture%20are%20restricted%20to%20orchard%20owners%2C%20tourism%20sustains%20hoteliers%2C%20houseboat%20owners%2C%20Shikarawallahs%20on%20the%20Dal%20Lake%2C%20taxi%20operators%2C%20pony%20wallahs%2C%20tourist%20guides%20and%20travel%20operators%20in%20addition%20to%20handicraft%20artisans%20like%20shawl%2C%20carpet%2C%20wood%20carving%20and%20papier%20machie%20craftsmen.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717140120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fhtup4ois_kashmir-tourism-generic_625x300_31_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-25-million-tourists-and-counting-in-2024-so-far-kashmir-to-set-new-record-5778662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tourist%20arrivals%20in%20Kashmir%20are%20set%20to%20break%20all%20previous%20records%20as%20more%2