0costs%20%2412%20a%20month%20per%20user.%20You%20can%20meet%20with%20up%20to%20150%20people%20at%20once.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Plus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0costs%20%2418%20a%20month%20per%20user.%20With%20this%2C%20you%20can%20meet%20with%20up%20to%20500%20people%20at%20once.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnterprise%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehas%20no%20fixed%20price%20and%20requires%20you%20to%20contact%20sales.%20At%20this%20level%2C%20you%20can%20meet%20with%20up%20to%201%2C000%20people%20at%20once.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20Google%20Workspace%20tier%20also%20comes%20with%20extra%20Google%20Drive%20storage%20space%20and%20advanced%20data%20security%20options.%20There%20are%20also%C2%A0versions%20built%20for%20schools%20and%20educators%2C%20which%20Google%20offers%20for%20free%20to%20certain%20institutions.%20Google%20Meet%20is%20also%20integrated%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-classroom%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Classroom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Google's%20online%20education%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20just%20an%20individual%20who%20wants%20to%20use%20Google%20Meet%20for%20your%20business%2C%20Google%20Workspace%20offers%20an%20individual%20plan%20for%20%249.99%20a%20month%2C%20or%20an%20annual%20package%20that%20costs%20%248.33%20per%20month%20for%2012%20months.%20This%20plan%20gives%20you%20meetings%20that%20can%20last%20up%20to%2024%20hours%2C%20as%20well%20as%20extra%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b98ad76d-3e44-4d04-9a6d-537281f74a30%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20join%20a%20Google%20Meet%20call%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20join%20a%20Google%20Meet%20session%20by%20using%20a%20code%20that's%20created%20when%20the%20event%20organizer%20schedules%20the%20meeting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20both%20the%20Meet%20mobile%20app%20and%20on%20a%20computer%2C%20simply%C2%A0pull%20up%20Google%20Meet%C2%A0and%20click%20or%20tap%20%26quot%3BUse%20a%20meeting%20cod