ke%20banana%2C%20garlic%2C%20ginger%2C%20and%20onion%20peels%20to%20fertilise%20soil%20and%20prevent%20the%20plant%20from%20fungal%20attacks.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20make%20the%20compost%2C%20collect%20peels%20in%20a%20bucket%20and%20add%20some%20water%20to%20it.%20After%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20strain%20the%20contents%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20clean%20water%20in%20a%20ratio%20of%201%3A2.%20Spray%20this%20fertiliser%20on%20all%20tray%20gardens%20every%20two%20to%20three%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharda%20says%20it%20takes%20her%20roughly%2020%20minutes%20to%20decorate%20the%20tray%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20I%20get%20bored%2C%20I%20recreate%20these%20tray%20gardens%20using%20the%20same%20plants%20and%20props.%20Just%20like%20kids%20play%20with%20their%20miniature%20dollhouses%2C%20I%20have%20my%20tray%20gardens.%20My%20friends%20say%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20my%20childhood%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Sharda%20Godara.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716813891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmini-tray-gardens-2-1716437290.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D350852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sharda%20Godara%20transformed%20her%20Faridabad%20home%20into%20a%20mini%20jungle%20with%201%2C000%20plants.%20She%20now%20enjoys%20crafting%20miniature%20tray%20gardens%20around%20various%20themes%2C%20and%20shares%20five%20steps%20to%20create%20them%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F350852%2Fhow-to-make-miniature-tray-gardens-at-home-steps-faridabad-sharda-godara-urban-gardener%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20%E2%80%98Eco%20Village%20Lady%E2%80%99%20of%20India%20Who%20Uses%20Solar%20Energy%20t